cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper presents a novel approach for program synthesis and semantic parsing using policy optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for policy optimization, which falls under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of memory buffers and distributed sampling, which are relevant to the categories of cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
